{
  "_comment": "Aegis Private Browser — Chromium enterprise managed policy, BALANCED level. Spec §6/§7/§9/§10. Keys are real Chromium enterprise policies (https://chromeenterprise.google/policies/). Emitted by browser-launcher from aegis-core PermissionPolicy + FingerprintPolicy; installed into the managed-policy directory INSIDE the Browser VM (Linux: /etc/chromium/policies/managed/). Normalization (not random spoofing) is applied by the Chromium fingerprint patch set, not by this file; this file governs account/telemetry/permission/network surface only. See ../README.md for the key-by-key mapping.",

